data.description: Move in ready 1772 sq. ft. home on 4.85 woodsy acres, 3 bedrooms, full guest bath, hardwoods in living, dining, family room, and master bedroom. (New) Kitchen counter tops, flooring & skylights, plus loads of storage & recessed lighting, spacious family room off kitchen. Oversized master bedroom suite w/5 pc bath plus walk in closet on private wing. Laundry/mud room comes with extra storage & closet, new furnace. Fully fenced backyard, Three out buildings for additional storage, 4.85 acres to roam about.
